Props :-    helps to communicate b/w components.
            it is a special keyword in react. 
            it stands for properties.
            data with props can be passed uni-directional.

state :-    it contains the data/info about the component.
            it is inbuilt react object.

            Manage state :  class component & functional component

            class component : ( this.state, this.setstate() )
            functional component : react hooks